name: s
description: probar funciones para el proyecto principal SFinanciero

scripts.db:migrate: cross-env NODE_ENV=development sequelize-cli db:migrate --config src/database/config/Sequelize.config.js --migrations-path src/database/migrations
scripts.db:seed: cross-env NODE_ENV=development sequelize-cli db:seed:all --config src/database/config/Sequelize.config.js --seeders-path src/database/seeders
scripts.db:migrate:undo: cross-env NODE_ENV=development sequelize-cli db:migrate:undo:all --config src/database/config/Sequelize.config.js --migrations-path src/database/migrations
